[Powassan is a municipality with a population of about 6400 residents in the Canadian province of Ontario, located near North Bay in the Almaguin Highlands region of Parry Sound District, about 330 km (205 mi) north of Toronto (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Powassan). A map showing the location of Powassan can be found at https://www.google.com/maps/place/Powassan,+ON+P0H+1Z0,+Canada. - Mod.ML]

